title: IDerivedPartFeatureData.ImportSheetMetalInformation
description: Gets or sets how to import sheet metal information with the derived part feature.
returns: How to import sheet metal information as defined in swImportSheetMetalInformation_e
remarks:
This property:
is valid only if the part being inserted is a sheet metal part.
is not valid if
IDerivedPartFeatureData::ImportCutListProperties
is set to true.
